The Knight Travails
===

An assignment project completed for a job interview.

Finds the Shortest Path for a Knight piece across a 8x8 Chess Board using the
A* Search Algorithm for navigating a graph.

### To build:

With the Makefile:

	> make

Without the Makefile:

	mkdir bin
	javac  src/*.java -sourcepath src/ -d bin/
	javac  src/chess/*.java -sourcepath src/ -d bin/
	javac  src/search/*.java -sourcepath src/ -d bin/

### To run:

	java -cp bin/ KnightTravails start goal [-all]
   
Usage:

	start, goal  Algebraic coordinate. (Form: [A-Z][0-9]) 
	-a,-all 	 (Optional) Use BreadthFirstSearch to display all paths
